OL,3,CUK's first safer drug consumption
OL,4,Cfacility offers hope to people `
OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FThe first safe drug consumption room
OL,8,Fin the UK will "offer hope" to
OL,9,Fhundreds of people, community leaders
OL,10,Fhave said.
OL,12,FThe Thistle will open in the east end
OL,13,Fof Glasgow on Monday at an existing
OL,14,FNHS enhanced drug treatment service.
OL,16,FScotland has the highest rate of drugs
OL,17,Fdeaths in Europe, with fatalities
OL,18,Frising by 12% in a year to 1,172 drug-
OL,19,Frelated deaths in 2023, of which 246
OL,20,Fwere in Glasgow.
