OL,3,CUK's first safer drug consumption
OL,4,Cfacility offers hope to people `
OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FThe #1 million facility will "offer
OL,8,Fhope" to an estimated 400 to 500
OL,9,Fpeople who inject in public in Glasgow
OL,10,Fcity centre every two weeks,
OL,11,Fcouncillor Allan Casey said.
OL,13,FIntravenous drug use creates pressure
OL,14,Fon the NHS, including amputations due
OL,15,Fto infected injection wounds, chronic
OL,16,Fobstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)
OL,17,Fand complex health problems, with
OL,18,Fpotentially critical health issues to
OL,19,Fbe addressed at an earlier stage at
OL,20,FThe Thistle.
