OL,3,CUK's first safer drug consumption
OL,4,Cfacility offers hope to people `
OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FCampaigners lobbied for almost a
OL,8,Fdecade for the facility after HIV
OL,9,Finfections surged in 2016 due to
OL,10,Fpeople injecting drugs but it was
OL,11,Fblocked by the Home Office until 2024.
OL,13,FMr Casey urged the Home Office to
OL,14,Fapprove a licence for drug testing
OL,15,Fbecause "people don't know what they
OL,16,Fare taking", with an explosion in
OL,17,Fsynthetic drugs blamed for the rise in
OL,18,Fdeaths, and after heroin contaminated
OL,19,Fwith anthrax caused 14 deaths in
OL,20,FGlasgow in 2009-10.
