OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FHe said: "There has been a war on
OL,8,Fdrugs in the UK for decades, but
OL,9,Fnobody is winning it apart from
OL,10,Fdealers.
OL,12,F"There needs to be a public health
OL,13,Fapproach ` having a drugs consumption
OL,14,Froom doesn't encourage people to take
OL,15,Fdrugs, the most important part is the
OL,16,Faftercare."
