OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FThe SNP councillor hopes to see
OL,8,Fsimilar facilities in Edinburgh and
OL,9,FBelfast, where both councils voted to
OL,10,Fset up centres, and described
OL,11,Fprovisions in The Thistle as "all
OL,12,Fsinging, all dancing" due to the scale
OL,13,Fof Glasgow's problems.
OL,15,FMr Casey said: "Between 400 to 500
OL,16,Fpeople regularly inject in public in
OL,17,FGlasgow city centre every two weeks.
OL,18,FThat's the target group we are hoping
OL,19,Fwill use this. If we get 20% that
OL,20,Fwould be a massive success.
