OL,7,F"In the last couple of weeks people
OL,8,Fhave been coming and we've been
OL,9,Ftelling them it's not open yet. It is
OL,10,Foffering hope to people."
OL,12,FLord Advocate Dorothy Bain KC said
OL,13,Fthere would be no public interest in
OL,14,Fprosecuting people injecting under
OL,15,Fmedical supervision in "injection
OL,16,Fbays" inside the building, which will
OL,17,Fbe open every day between 9am and 9pm.
