OL,3,CUK's first safer drug consumption
OL,4,Cfacility offers hope to people `
OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FThe clinical environment in the Hunter
OL,8,FStreet Health Centre includes a
OL,9,Fsmoking area, chatrooms, i-Pads so
OL,10,Fpeople can contact family and a lounge
OL,11,Fwith books and hot drinks, and to
OL,12,Foffer support with housing and
OL,13,Fbenefits as well as healthcare in a
OL,14,Fwelcoming environment.
OL,16,FService manager Lynn MacDonald said
OL,17,FGlaswegian users inject drugs which
OL,18,Fwould not typically be seen elsewhere
OL,19,Fin the UK.
