OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FIt is expected about 40% of visitors
OL,8,Fwill be women, with efforts made to be
OL,9,Fprovide hairdryers and contraception,
OL,10,Fand dry clothes for both sexes.
OL,12,FMrs MacDonald said: "There is a huge
OL,13,Famount of cocaine injected in Glasgow,
OL,14,Fabout a 50-50 split.
OL,16,F"With heroin, people are injecting
OL,17,Fthree, four times a day ` with cocaine
OL,18,Fit could be 10, 12, 14 times, often
OL,19,Finjecting into the same sites because
OL,20,Fthey can get access.
