OL,7,F"People are concerned it is going to
OL,8,Fbring drugs into the area but it is
OL,9,Falready here ` it is very visible. It
OL,10,Fis not hidden. We are talking about
OL,11,Fpeople, not addicts or users. The
OL,12,Fdrugs are a tiny part of their lives."
OL,14,FDr Priyadarshi said: "The sort of
OL,15,Fissues we are aware of are injecting
OL,16,Fwounds, particularly from injection of
OL,17,Fcocaine, which we will hopefully be
OL,18,Fable to address early on, so we can
OL,19,Fprevent difficult surgical operations.
