OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,F"Studies show that someone who is 40
OL,8,Fto 45 years old may have the health of
OL,9,Fa 75-to-80 year old with multiple
OL,10,Fdiseases. It would be a fairytale for
OL,11,Fme to say we can make it better
OL,12,Fovernight, but we do want to help
OL,13,Fpeople engage with healthcare.
OL,15,F"In a year's time I hope we will have
OL,16,Fprevented deaths and hospital
OL,17,Fadmissions ` this service supports a
OL,18,Freduction in ambulance callouts, and
OL,19,Fattendance at A&E with preventative
OL,20,Fcare. I think it is much needed."
